%% ====================================================================
%% Sequence 03: Task List (today's tasks + overdue always shown + authz filter)
%% Task Management System v1.3
%% ====================================================================
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as Member ユーザー
  participant Browser as ブラウザ
  participant Sec as Spring Security
  participant Filter as TenantContextFilter
  participant Ctrl as TaskController
  participant UC as ListTasksUseCase
  participant AuthZ as TaskAuthorizationDomainService
  participant TaskRepo as TaskRepositoryImpl
  participant StakeholderRepo as StakeholderRepositoryImpl
  participant DB as MySQL

  User->>Browser: ダッシュボード表示
  Browser->>Ctrl: GET /api/tasks?targetDate=2026-05-12&includeOverdue=true<br/>(Bearer + X-Tenant-Id: 11)
  Sec->>Filter: 認証OK
  Filter->>Filter: TenantContext.set(tenantId=11, userId=1, role=MEMBER)
  Filter->>Ctrl: forward
  Ctrl->>UC: execute(ListTasksQuery)

  Note over UC,DB: --- 期限切れ未完了タスク取得 ---
  UC->>TaskRepo: findOverdueOpen(tenantId=11, today=2026-05-12)
  TaskRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks<br/>WHERE tenant_id=11 AND deleted_at IS NULL<br/>AND due_date < '2026-05-12'<br/>AND status != 'DONE'
  DB-->>TaskRepo: 期限切れタスク 7件
  TaskRepo-->>UC: List<Task>

  Note over UC,DB: --- 当日タスク取得 ---
  UC->>TaskRepo: findByTenantAndDate(tenantId=11, date=2026-05-12)
  TaskRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks<br/>WHERE tenant_id=11 AND deleted_at IS NULL<br/>AND due_date = '2026-05-12'<br/>ORDER BY due_date, priority
  DB-->>TaskRepo: 本日タスク 23件
  TaskRepo-->>UC: List<Task>

  Note over UC,DB: --- 関係者タスクID一括フェッチ (N+1回避) ---
  UC->>StakeholderRepo: findTaskIdsByUser(userId=1, tenantId=11)
  StakeholderRepo->>DB: SELECT task_id FROM task_stakeholders<br/>WHERE user_id=1 AND tenant_id=11
  DB-->>StakeholderRepo: task_id リスト
  StakeholderRepo-->>UC: Set<Long> stakeholderTaskIds

  Note over UC,AuthZ: --- 公開範囲フィルタを適用 ---
  Note over AuthZ: 参照認可の詳細ルールは TaskAuthorizationDomainService が SSOT<br/>(基本設計書 §6.2.1 参照)
  loop 各 task について
    UC->>AuthZ: canBeViewedBy(task, userId=1, role=MEMBER, stakeholderTaskIds)
    AuthZ-->>UC: ✓ 参照可 / ✗ 除外
  end

  Note over UC: --- 各タスクに editable / deletable フラグ付与 ---
  loop 各 visibleTask
    UC->>AuthZ: canBeEditedBy(task, userId, role) → boolean
  end

  UC-->>Ctrl: TaskPage(content, overdueCount=7, ...)
  Ctrl-->>Browser: 200 OK + JSON
  Browser-->>User: 期限切れ7件 + 本日タスクを表示<br/>(編集ボタンは所有者のみ表示)
